| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1403 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2d8de4a3-e014-54e0-8e81-946ac44879b4"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
